description:
Binned ggplot2 color scales using the color palettes generated by qualitative_hcl. These scales are provided
for completeness. It is not normally a good idea to color a continuous, binned variable using a qualitative scale.
example_call: scale_colour_binned_qualitative(palette = NULL, c1 = NULL, l1 = NULL, h1 = NULL, h2 = NULL,
